details: What it is: A new multidimensional texture palette for cheeks inspired by Natasha’s famous Glow system.What it does:This cheek palette was created with a diamond-like sparkle, based on Natasha's idea of a new generation of glow. Use it to play and achieve a wide range of finishes and looksfrom natural to extreme. Create a duo-chrome or diamond glow. The palette also includes a new cream blush, as well as Natasha’s classic powder blush.This set contains:- 0.25 oz/ 7 g Glow Cream- 0.25 oz/ 7 g Diamond Powder- 0.25 oz/ 7 g Cream Blush- 0.25 oz/ 7 g Powder Blush- 0.25 oz/ 7 g Duo Chrome Highlighter- 0.25 oz/ 7 g Extreme GlowWhat it is formulated WITHOUT:- ParabensWhat else you need to know: This palette is free of talc free, UV filters, D5, and oil. It is also cruelty-free

details:
What it is:
A highlighting duo for the cheeks, eyes, and face to achieve glowing skin. 

What it does:
 Sweep Sheer Highlighting Duo in Reflects Gilt features a pair of shimmering rose and yellow gold hues that are inspired by the sunrise and the sunset. Embossed with TOM FORD logo, it imparts a light-reflective finish for bronzed, glowing skin. This duo features a versatile cheek and face highlighter with a radiant eye shadow, and the shades can be applied wet for a soft veil of color, or dry for a pop of vibrancy. Wear these shades alone or together for non-streaking, stay-true color that blends easily.
ingredients:
Tom Ford is a celebrated American designer who launched his brand in 2005 with a mission to redefine modern luxury. With menswear, women’s wear, accessories, eyewear, and beauty, TOM FORD is synonymous with sexy, timeless elegance and superior workmanship.
Visit the TOM FORD boutique

details: What it is: A powder blush with a color-rich formula that glides onto skin with the comfort of a cream.What Else You Need to Know: This sumptuous powder blush is formulated with spherical pearls and rich emollients that glide onto skin with the comfort of a cream. It achieves outstanding luminosity and a velvety transparency. Six buildable shades allow for versatile color layering, from a sexy glow to a more dramatic, color-rich look.

details: What it is: A palette of six lightweight pigments encapsulated in a breakthrough formula that delivers a sheer wash of color to accentuate all skin tones.What Else You Need to Know: NARS’s Color Clarity Complex is a lightweight powder encapsulated in a clear base that builds effortlessly and blends seamlessly onto any skin tone, revealing color in its truest form. This unique formula allows pigment to be built up while keeping a luxurious, non-chalky texture. It can be worn wet or dry for different effects. Apply it dry for a silky veil of second-skin color. Apply it wet for a high-impact glow. Shades can be worn individually or blended together for multidimensional sheen.This Palette Contains:- 6 x 0.1 oz/ 2.96 g Blush in Tell All (pearlescent golden pink), Now or Never (satin terracotta), Give it Away (satin nude), Make You Mine (satin peach), Come Hither (satin watermelon), New Fling (satin fuchsia)

details: What it is: An ultimate glow palette inspired by Natasha Denona’s bestselling Diamond & Blush Palette, featuring some of her bestselling shades and formulas. Ingredient Callouts: Free of parabens. This product is also cruelty-free and gluten-free.What Else You Need to Know: This palette contains a range of exquisite formulas. The hydrating, velvety cream blush is designed to give your skin a healthy flush of color. Glow Cream Base is a hydrating, luminous cream highlight with real crushed mineral pearls to give your skin the ultimate glow. Duo Glow is a multipurpose, duo-chrome highlighting powder with real, crushed, mineral duo-chrome pearls to give your skin a supernatural, shade-shifting glow. Extreme Glow is a multidimensional, sparkling, creamy powder highlight with a soft-focus, HD finish and a velvety-smooth texture.This Palette Contains:- Glow Cream Base in Peach (natural peach)- Cream Blush in Fuchsia (deep cherry red with a subtle bronze shine)- Glow Extreme in Light Rose (nude champagne)- Duo Glow in Vibrant, Golden Coral (vibrant coral with golden champagne)

details:
What it is:A multipurpose, long-wearing, creamy lip and cheek duo with a luxurious matte finish.   
What it does: Long-wearing yet creamy and moisturizing, this innovative formulation provides blendable and buildable colorperfect for day and night. Apply as a cream eyeshadow for the ultimate multitasker.                                                    

What else you need to know:This product is cruelty-free, vegan, and free of synthetic fragrances and gluten.  lilah b. embodies the philosophy of With less, you are more with their streamlined multipurpose collection of color. Simplify your beauty routine with their healthy, good-for-you formulations and achieve a finished, flawless look with fewer products. The luxurious formulas are enriched with aloe, agar, and other beneficial botanicals to deliver a healthy, glowing finish, and come housed in sleek, modern, signature stones.

Clean at Sephora
Clean at Sephora is formulated without a list of over 50 ingredients, including sulfates (SLS and SLES), parabens, phthalates, and more. For the full list, check out the Ingredients tab.

details: What it is: A dual-purpose lip-to-cheek creamy color stick.What it does:Beach Sticks can be used on cheeks as blush or on lips as a soft tint. A key ingredient, ceramidone, acts like a poly-filler to plump up and refill the look of skin, giving you a flawless surface, while creamy polymers moisturize the skin. Highly pigmented and shimmering, the formula blends easily, illuminating skin with brilliant, color-saturated pigments for an irresistible summer glow. Light-diffusing spheres soft-focus imperfections and bring radiance to the face, for the perfect summer flash of color. A fusion of waxes hydrate your skin for a dewy, supple finish.What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Parabens- Sulfates
